Dear Ladies / Gentlemen,

The Beijing Qiaosen Gift Services Co. (Ltd.) was established in 1999 and together with an expanding Chinese economy it has shown positive growth over the past few years.

The company is a multiple service business venture that specializes in exhibition services, business gifts or promotional items planning and providing. The company has broad experience in layout, design and construction of exhibition displays. We also help companies organize conferences as well as providing business-space display stands. Our services are professionally packaged with the help of our specialized staff, up to date technology, unique ideas and vast experience. The professional staffs from design specialists, account-servicing people, marketing teams, project teams and operation managers whom in charge of various sections on carpentry, studio graphics and AV as well.

In the beginning the company's key function was the supply of promotional merchandise tailored to our customers needs and some of our clients include large enterprises .Our product range now includes over 5000 independently sourced products. Promotional merchandise is our key service and we have a large number of companies on our books with which we have had business dealings in the past.

Conveniently located in ChaoYang district, the central business district of Beijing, We have shown substantial growth in 2003 and have won the praise of many large multinationals such as Siemens, GEMS, Schneider Electric, ABB, Nokia, China National Medicines Corp.Ltd., Pricewaterhouse, GCC, Group Corp., Agree Technology, Peak Pacific Investment Co. Ltd., Ctrip Co.etc.
      
Our Service Steps:
       1) Plan business activities effectively and creatively.
       2) Design and construct exhibition booths and stages.
       3) Organise conferences.
       4) Source business gifts and promotional items.
       5) Offer a comprehensive service tailored to the needs of individual customers.
       6) Provide professional products and services.  
       7) Source and supply a wide range of products.
       8) Our efficiency ensures quality products.
       9) Our products are guaranteed.
10) We ensure timely delivery.

Business gifts and promotional items including: 
       Business products, Daily life products, Travel products, Office stationery,
       Promotional articles, Art & Crafts, Ornaments, Recreation & Entertainment,
       Trophy products, Household appliances, Lighting devices, Radios, Perpetual 
       calendars, Desk decorations, Bags & Briefcases, Clock & Watch series, Leather
       products, Tools, Garments.

Our advantages are as follows:
1. Our knowledge of the domestic markets. We have set up a serving system that makes our business more efficient i.e. designing, processing, purchasing and assembling according to the clients requirements.

2. Our company succeeds in surviving through creativity and quality. We realize the demand for competitively priced quality products and they are designed and produced by reputable companies.

3. We observe government policies, laws and regulations and follow the trade practices whilst adhering to the principle of mutual benefit and honoring the agreements established with our clients. 

4. To cultivate our employees into a competent team that is highly efficient, passionate, creative, good at learning, and full of cooperation spirit. In addition, our employees should have the sense of social responsibility, enterprise honor and self-achievement.

5. To build our unique enterprise culture that is full of time spirit .To advocate integrity & professionalism, cooperation & sharing, and creativity & service. 

6. To possess our own highly recognized brand 



We believe that the client always comes first, creation is our power and perfect service is our soul. Our motto is: Sincere service, client satisfaction, distinct creation and professional team building. Choosing Beijing G & J Exhibition Co.Ltd is the right choice, we will not let you down. 

We look forward to helping you expand your business. Thanks for your attention.



